::Feline::

She smiled and looked at Zardus.  She took the tip of her tail and 
stroked the side of Zardus' face.  She smiled and purred. She knew 
that she had something that the other bots wanted.  And she knew how 
to use it. (Satalite link to HBO helps)
She put her hand on his shoulder and rubber her finge on his neck.
She purred in his ear and walked along with him to the mess hall.  
She had her tail around his shoulders so all the other bots could see 
her with him.
